Program: The Documentary
Title: US Election 2012: Is America Working?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p010hb0z
Last Broadcast Date: Sun 4 Nov 2012
BBC World Have Your Say's Ros Atkins travels across the USA to find out if America is working. We hear from farmers, factory workers, actors, truckers, members of the military and office workers ahead of the presidential election. (Image: A baby with an American flag. Credit: REUTERS/Shannon Stapleton) Show less